results.title: Peter Parker: Spider-Man (1999) #11
results.description: THE EIGHTH DAY PART 3 The Wager of Octessence has chosen its eighth and final Exemplar, Stonecutter. Now, the only thing that stands between Earth and Armageddon is the combined might of Spider-Man, Iron and Thor!
